    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "V8013N\nFLY- EASTERN AIR LINES A02\nNY315V}\nSEEING IS BELIEVING\nEastern's New-Type Con-\nstellation demonstrating\nits amazing power-flying\neasily and smoothly on\none of its 4 mighty en-\ngines. The world's most\npowerful and dependable\nairliner. Read other side.",
      "Taken from the new film, \"Air Power is Peace\nPower\" by Captain Eddie V. Rickenbacker,\nEastern Air Line's New-Type Constellation dem-\nonstrates its \"Tried and Proven\" dependability,\nits tremendous reserve of power.\nIts four engines, totaling 10,000 horsepower\ngive this plane unequaled ability to take-off and\nland with great dependability and fly swiftly\nand smoothly. It's truly the World's most Power-\nful, most Dependable Airliner.\nHAND TO FLIGHT ATTENDANT FOR MAILING\n3-\nPOST CARD\nStamp Here\n2015/166,0650"
